title: Turkey's Erdogan visits quake region as anger grows over rescue speed
Crowds erupt as family rescued from rubble in Syria
content: Crowds cheered as a family of two adults and four children were pulled from rubble in Idlib, Syria by the White Helmets rescue group, which operates in rebel-controlled areas..

title: Putin 'supplied' MH17 missile - investigators
content: Prosecutors said there is evidence that Mr Putin decided to provide the missile to Moscow-backed separatists.. There is no suggestion that Mr Putin was involved in ordering the aircraft be shot down. .
